e right spaces, in the right moments, in the right time.\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 1038, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the penalty box\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"the right spaces\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"the right moments\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s going to take a little bit of time.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The U.S.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s lone goal came from the familiar frontline duo of Smith and Mallory Swanson.\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"time.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1086}, {\"ngram\": \"The U.S.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s lone goal\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"the familiar frontline duo\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"Mallory Swanson\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two, along with winger Trinity Rodman and attacking midfielder Rose Lavelle, played off each other with a palpable fluidity, creating a number of dangerous chances in the final third.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI was really happy for Soph \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 I thought her and Mal were so dynamic,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Hayes said.\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1205, \"end\": 1219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Trinity Rodman\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\"}, {\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Lavelle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rose Lavelle\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\",